Dear U2.Com Member,

The Elevation 2001 Tour is to run on into December. Eight more US dates have
just been announced which begin to go on sale from this weekend. (Time
constraints mean that a U2.Com pre-sale is not possible for these shows.)

The additional dates are Sacramento (November 20th), Phoenix (November
23rd), Dallas (November 25th), Kansas (November 27th), St Louis (November
28th), Atlanta (November 30th), Tampa (December 1st) and Miami (December
2nd).  See a complete list of dates, venues and on-sale information below -
and also at http://cc.com/


And in other U2 news...

* The awards season continues unabated.  The band are up for a batch
of awards in the MY VH-I Music Awards. Vote here -
http://www.vh1.com/mymusic/2001/

U2 are also  nominated in the Top Tour and the Top Rock categories in
the first ever BBC Top of the Pops awards. Vote here -
http://www.bbc.co.uk/totp/features/totp_awards/index.shtml

* 'What's Going On?', the all-star cover version of the Marvin Gaye classic,
is now in stores - buy it online here -
http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/B00005QJDH/107-3739627-8944567

But complementing the EP there is also a 'Town Hall Tour' this month
bringing together local experts and activists on global debt  and the AIDS
crisis. The events include  unique video of Bono and other members of
Artists Against AIDS Worldwide. For cities on the tour check our story -
http://www.u2.com/lite/index_whatsgoingon.html


* Meanwhile the new U2.Com community area  - Zootopia - is busier than
ever with additional features just launched while the U2.Com store
continues to carry the latest Elevation Tour product.

Zootopia - http://zootopia.u2.com/
U2 Shop - http://shop.u2.com/


* And so to those new dates in full, which begin to go on sale this Saturday
November 10th (all times are local):

November 20th - Sacremento, Arco Arena - On sale Nov 10th, 10am

November 23rd - Phoenix, America West Arena - On sale Nov 10th, 10am

November 25th - Dallas, Reunion Arena - On sale Nov 10th, 12noon

November 27th - Kansas City, Kemper Arena - On sale Nov 10th, 10am

November 28th - St Louis, Savvis Center - On sale Nov 10th, 10am

November 30th - Atlanta, Philips Arena - On sale Nov 10th, 10am

December 1st - Tampa, Ice Palace - On sale Nov 17th, 10am

December 2nd - Miami, American Airlines Arena - On sale Nov 17th, 10am


Best wishes


